Latest news: I installed the new panel and it seems to be working.
It might just turn off at sunset, but let's wait and see.
By the way, I'm using the ping integration in Home Assistant to keep an eye on whether it's connected or not.
The round-trip time is 102 ms. Not great, but not that bad.
